<%- include('layouts/header') %>

<!-- Vicharan Details Start -->
<div class="container-xxl py-5">
    <div class="container" style="border: 6px solid coral;border-radius: 15px;background-color: lightyellow;">
        <div class="text-center mx-auto mb-5 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.1s" style="max-width: 600px;">
            <h1 class="mb-3"><%= (vicharanData.title).toUpperCase() %></h1>
        </div>
        <div class="row justify-content-md-center g-4">
            <div class="col-lg-10 col-md-12 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.1s">
                <div class="position-relative">
                    <img class="img-fluid center-block rounded" src="/<%= vicharanData.photo %>" alt="" style="box-shadow: 0 4px 8px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2), 0 6px 20px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.19);">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row justify-content-md-center g-4">
            <div class="col-lg-10 col-md-12 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.1s">
                <div class="h-100 d-flex flex-column justify-content-center">
                    <h2><br>Shri Sanatan Jain Dharma Shrimad Rajchandra Ashram</h2>
                    <h5>The Ashram is established by Pujya Shri Laghurajswami (P.P. Prabhushriji) in Vikram Era 1976</h5>
                    <p>Age: More than 100 years ago. Shrimad Rajchandraji himself had forecasted that this will be a Punya Bhumi.<br>
                    P.P. Prabushriji was endorsed by Shrimad as a True Gyaani. Shrimad handed over to P.P. Prabhushriji for enforcement of a True religion and then P.P. Prabhushriji handed it over to P. Bramhchariji. Thereafter, no further handover has been seen, as this place is reserved only for Aatmagyaani.<br>
                    But both Prabhushriji and P. Bramhchariji never considered them as a Guru but endorsed Shrimadji as Our Only Guru.<br><br>
                    <span style="font-family:Comic Sans MS, sans-serif; font-weight:580; line-height:1.5; color:yellowgreen;font-size:25px;">Motto of this Ashram to get burn the seed of all the sorrows majorly birth and death cycle.</span>
                    </p>
                    <h2><br>Uniqueness of the Ashram</h2>
                    <p>Despite no Physical Pratyaksh Guru but what is definitely present here is Aagya of a Pratyaksh True Guru.<br>
                    The whole Aaradhna Kram of more than 10 hours is designed by P.P. Prabhushriji. There has mainly been no change in the kram since more than 100 years.<br>
                    The “Pratishta” of this Ashram was done under the supervision of P.P. Prabhushriji.<br>
                    The Aaradhna Kram comprises of Devotional Bhakti, Taatvik Bhakti, Aalochana / Pratikraman, Various Holy Bhaavnas, Satsang etc. This is the Agya Kram given by Gyani.<br>
                    The Ashram has a huge library of Religious Books.<br>
                    Prabhushriji himself said that this place is a strongest reason for Samadhi Maran. He has set a 36 Maala Aaradhna Kram for Samadhi Maran which is a sure shot reason for the Samadhi Maran.
                    </p>
                    <h2><br>Facilities:</h2>
                    <p><span style="font-size: 18px;color:hotpink;"><b><u>Stay:</u></b></span> A huge dharmshaala having rooms with essential amenities.<br>
                    <span style="font-size: 18px;color:hotpink;"><b><u>Food:</u></b></span> A huge Bhojanshala which provides food to each and everyone coming inside the ashram
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row justify-content-md-center g-4">
            <div class="col-lg-10 col-md-12 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.1s">
                <h2>Ashram Darshan</h2>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="column">
                <img class="img-fluid rounded fitImageEqually" src="/a1.jpg" onclick="expandImage(this);">
            </div>
            <div class="column">
                <img class="img-fluid rounded fitImageEqually" src="/a2.jpg" onclick="expandImage(this);">
            </div>
            <div class="column">
                <img class="img-fluid rounded fitImageEqually" src="/a3.jpg" onclick="expandImage(this);">
            </div>
            <div class="column">
                <img class="img-fluid rounded fitImageEqually" src="/a4.jpg" onclick="expandImage(this);">
            </div>
            <div class="column">
                <img class="img-fluid rounded fitImageEqually" src="/a5.jpg" onclick="expandImage(this);">
            </div>
            <div class="column">
                <img class="img-fluid rounded fitImageEqually" src="/a6.jpg" onclick="expandImage(this);">
            </div>
            <div class="column">
                <img class="img-fluid rounded fitImageEqually" src="/a7.jpg" onclick="expandImage(this);">
            </div>
            <div class="column">
                <img class="img-fluid rounded fitImageEqually" src="/a8.jpg" onclick="expandImage(this);">
            </div>
            <div class="column">
                <img class="img-fluid rounded fitImageEqually" src="/a9.jpg" onclick="expandImage(this);">
            </div>
            <div class="column">
                <img class="img-fluid rounded fitImageEqually" src="/a10.jpg" onclick="expandImage(this);">
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- The expanding image container -->
        <div class="imageContainer">
          <!-- Close the image -->
          <span style="color: black;" onclick="this.parentElement.style.display='none'" class="closebtn">&times;</span>

          <!-- Expanded image -->
          <img class="img-fluid center-block rounded" id="expandedImg" style="width: -webkit-fill-available;margin-bottom: 10px;">
        </div>

    </div>
</div>
<!-- Vicharan Details End -->

<script type="text/javascript">
    //image expander in vicharanDetails
    function expandImage(imgs) {
      // Get the expanded image
      var expandImg = document.getElementById("expandedImg");
      
      // Use the same src in the expanded image as the image being clicked on from the grid
      expandImg.src = imgs.src;
      
      // Show the container element (hidden with CSS)
      expandImg.parentElement.style.display = "block";
}
</script>

